          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"><Array as="points"><mxPoint x="970" y="485" /><mxPoint x="970" y="110" /></Array></mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>

        <mxCell id="p1foot" value="&lt;font color=&quot;#888888&quot;&gt;데이터: MultiHiertt dev (post-audit gold, 2026-07-07 이후 재측정본만 사용) · 결과 수치는 2페이지&lt;/font&gt;" style="text;html=1;fontSize=10;align=left;" vertex="1" parent="1">
